nitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1904-07-28" n="01">28. 7. 1904</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb415">Aussee</placeName><date when="1904-07-29">29. 7. 1904</date></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1904-07-11_01">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 11. 7. 1904</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1904-08-17_02">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 17. 8. 1904</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
